val oildrillingrig = mods.modularmachinery.RecipeBuilder.newBuilder("machinethree", "machinethree", 1000);
oildrillingrig.addEnergyPerTickInput(100);
oildrillingrig.addItemInput(<minecraft:dirt>);
oildrillingrig.addItemOutput(<minecraft:sapling:5> *6);
oildrillingrig.build();

val jichujiqiwaike = mods.modularmachinery.RecipeBuilder.newBuilder("machinethree", "machinethree", 100);
jichujiqiwaike.addEnergyPerTickInput(10);
jichujiqiwaike.addItemInput(<minecraft:dirt:1>);
jichujiqiwaike.addItemOutput(<minecraft:sapling:5> *9);
jichujiqiwaike.build();
第二个无效，第一个被加载。
求解嘤嘤嘤!
注：当json配方以及crafttweaker魔改配方第一个有效配方被删除时，第二个能够被游戏加载。
